# This is a Windows CrossGate server: data files are GBK-encoded with CRLF line
# endings, and the engine's parsers depend on that exact byte layout.
# Disable git's automatic line-ending normalization on every platform so the
# repo always checks out byte-for-byte identical (a LF/CRLF mismatch corrupts
# data parsing, e.g. all enemies collapsing to id=1).
* -text

# Binary assets: never diff or convert.
*.db3 binary
